Luke: Mary Joseph birreji Bethlehem, maloerroe milala.
Galitjjilik-birra birroenmijing maloerroema ayppara majumatjju buliki giyani igun.
Bibi batbing igun, damoywa banimilap gujurrbirra bani birriging, bamarap marilma mayoema box buliki giyani igun.
Mary Joseph birreji Bethlehem, maloerroe milala.
Galitjjilik-birra birroenmijing maloerroema ayppara majumatjju buliki giyani igun.
Bibi batbing igun, damoywa banimilap gujurrbirra bani birriging, bamarap marilma mayoema box buliki giyani igun.
Yaagwa damunggwa galaguk, iwa boedlirra marilma ayppara sheep girrimalkkanyini.
Angel gulkkwa Heaven gumiling, bini boedlirra ayppara balarr guleji gulp God boemiling bilppil gugam, boedlirra birrijalming.
Angel bigam “Gurrijalmam garrip! Maan batjji gurrunggura ankiyak maan batjji binyolkkirra ankiyak.”

Ilan-gwa banitba nimba batbing yaagwa Bethlehem ayppara gunijirrgwa David guligi ing-gwa yaagwa, gurri bugurrmirili damoywa banimilap, biyung marilma mayoema box buliki ankiyak, imuling gudluwa gurriga Biyanaba gunyigamalkkany, Biyanaba Christ boedla, God gunyigilijoerr Saviour.
